{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b923374311","title":"吴德给唐锡阳的信","origin":"北京政法学院政法公社《内部参考》第二期。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"19919fb7c3","index":0,"year":1966,"month":11,"day":29,"articleId":"b923374311"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"7f0393737e","name":"吴德","type":"人物"},{"id":"877762393f","name":"两条路线斗争","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"300ec78d67","name":"吴德"},{"id":"8f866b62fc","name":"唐锡阳"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"421e7afd10","type":"title","text":"吴德给唐锡阳的信","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b923374311"},{"id":"9893d272c4","type":"authors","text":"吴德唐锡阳","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b923374311"},{"id":"e6e9338a56","type":"appellation","text":"锡阳同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b923374311"},{"id":"7dc53c764b","type":"paragraph","text":"你的女孩和你给我的关于郑兆南同志的一些材料，我都看过了。读了这些材料，我很沉痛。经过了解，郑兆南同志是革命的，是一位好同志。必须彻底批判资产阶级反动路线。我们悼念郑兆南同志，一定给郑兆南同志彻底平反，恢复名誉。对这一案件，市委要严肃处理。望你保重身体，照顾好孩子。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b923374311"},{"id":"fbd6a13e65","type":"paragraph","text":"顺致","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b923374311"},{"id":"2a6e493994","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级的革命敬礼！","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b923374311"},{"id":"f4aa00f2cc","type":"paragraph","text":" 吴德十一月二十九日","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b923374311"},{"id":"361b0502b7","type":"subtitle","text":"唐锡阳致中央文革小组的信","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b923374311"},{"id":"d440202a99","type":"appellation","text":"中央文革小组：","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b923374311"},{"id":"72448886e6","type":"paragraph","text":"这是我妻子郑兆南的两封遗书。她重伤后于九月三日回家，九月八日在第六医院吐血身死。前一封信寄给了李雪峰同志，后一封信交给了吴德同志。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b923374311"},{"id":"f6d7dd0392","type":"paragraph","text":"我认为这是当前两条路线斗争的一个严重反映，因此抄寄一份给你们，做为研究情况，指导运动的一个参考，并请敦促市委正确处理这个问题。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b923374311"},{"id":"d79036a3a1","type":"paragraph","text":"革命的敬礼","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b923374311"},{"id":"9278b10047","type":"paragraph","text":" 北京日报  唐锡阳十月十九日","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b923374311"},{"id":"b02373d042","type":"appellation","text":"","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b923374311"}],"page":{"id":"dc5ba2021b","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b923374311","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}